data.title: “Jannat” tugboat returns to work in Misrata Free Zone
data.meta_description: The Misrata Free Zone has announced that the tugboat “Jannat” is back into service after it was hit in a collision with one of the ships docked at the port of Misrata Free Zone in October 2020. The Misrata Free Zone indicated that the maintenance work included introducing new technologies to the tugboat in line with modern requirements to increase its efficiency.
data.text:
The Misrata Free Zone has announced that the tugboat “Jannat” is back into service after it was hit in a collision with one of the ships docked at the port of Misrata Free Zone in October 2020.

The Misrata Free Zone indicated that the maintenance work included introducing new technologies to the tugboat in line with modern requirements to increase its efficiency.
